header.gameNote: NCAA Women's Championship pres. by Capital One - River Walk Region - 2nd Round

videos.headline: Brown sinks nice and-1 bucket for Michigan
videos.description: Danielle Rauch lobs a pass to Leigha Brown, who finishes with the bucket and the foul for Michigan.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Brown sinks nice and-1 bucket for Michigan) 2021/3/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Hillmon scores back-to-back buckets for Michigan
videos.description: Naz Hillmon grabs a rebound after a miss and ends up scoring for Michigan. Kasiyahna Kushkituah answers with a bucket on the other end for Tennessee, but Hillmon scores again right after that.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Hillmon scores back-to-back buckets for Michigan) 2021/3/23 ESHEET

videos.headline: Johnson steals and Brown scores to pad Michigan's lead
videos.description: Akienreh Johnson steals the ball and gives it to Leigha Brown, who scores another Michigan bucket vs. Tennessee.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_One-Play (Johnson steals and Brown scores to pad Michigan's lead) 2021/3/23 ESHEET
